==個人風格==
一名多才多藝的[[中場#防守中場|防守]]或[[中場#中前衛|正中場]]，具有良好視野和整體技術，蒂亚戈最為人所知的是他的工作率，韌性以及攔截能力，正如他在獲得控球權以後的分球能力。這些出眾凡能力為他在里昂效力的期間獲得「the washing machine」的稱號。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gazzetta.it/Calcio/Primo_Piano/2009/02/13/sissoko.shtml|title=Sissoko: "Sono La Piovra"|trans_title=Sissoko: "I am The Octopus"|publisher=[[La_Gazzetta_dello_Sport|La Gazzetta dello Sport]]|language=it|author1=Alberto Mauro|date=13 February 2009|accessdate=23 November 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tuttosport.com/calcio/champions_league/2014/09/30-307882/Champions+League+Atletico%3A+Tiago,+un+passato+Juve.+%C2%ABNon+vi+capivo...%C2%BB|title=Champions League Atletico: Tiago, un passato Juve. «Non vi capivo...»|trans_title=Champions League Atletico: Tiago, a Juve past. "I didn't understand you..."|publisher=Tuttosport|language=it|author1=Guido Vaciago|date=30 September 2014|accessdate=30 November 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141002094530/http://www.tuttosport.com/calcio/champions_league/2014/09/30-307882/Champions+League+Atletico:+Tiago,+un+passato+Juve.+%C2%ABNon+vi+capivo...%C2%BB|archivedate=2014年10月2日}}</ref>

